Controlling Program Flow

selection
if, if-else, nested if, switch statement, conditional operator ?;

loops
for, while, do-while, continue and break, infinite and nested loops

if statement
  if(expr) 
    statement;

or 
  if(expression) {
    statement
  }

the latter "{}" is called a block statement. 

if- else

if(expr)
  statement1;
else if
  statement2
else
  statement3;

nested if statement
if(expr)
  if(expr)
    statement1;
  else
    statement2;

switch case
